# Overview

- **Stack**: Angular 20 standalone components; similar setup to `car-client` but focused on the public catalog variant (no embedded admin console).
- **Routing**: Defined in `app.routes.ts`; wraps marketing pages (`/home`, `/cars/search`, `/car/:id`, `/team`, etc.) inside `LayoutComponent`.
- **Shared Blocks**: UI pieces live under `blocks/**` (car card, contact form, layout). Reuse these components when extending pages to keep styling consistent.
- **Configuration**: `config/cities.config.ts` and `config/seo.config.ts` centralise city metadata and meta tags; adjust them instead of editing components directly.

