# Development Notes

- Local API host lives in `environment.ts` (`http://localhost:3001`); production builds rely on `environment.prod.ts`.
- Prefer standalone components and co-located SCSS; when adding new sections, update routing titles for SEO and use `config/seo.config.ts` for meta tags.
